---
title: Southwestern Black Bean Cakes with Baby Gem Avocado Salad and Lime Crema
description: These perfect little cake are so unassuming until you take your first bite. Crispy browning on the outside and creamy mashed beans within are oh-so-yummy. Also, can we share how obsessed we are with this lime dressing?
